Rotten Netflix
================================
A Chrome extension that appends Rotten Tomatoes scores to Netflix movie pages


Overview
--------------------------
This was intended to help people searching for movies on Netflix, and are interested in the Rotten Tomatoes score.


Features
--------------------------

* Appends the Rotten Tomato critic and audience score to Netflix movie pages
* Score is a link to the movie's Rotten Tomato page


Installation (for Users)
--------------------------

Just visit the Chrome app store and install. 
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/jgmifidejldikemoilinmhnedpnghakn


Installation (for Developers)
-------------------------

Visit https://github.com/tcomben/Rotten-Netflix to get the latest

Sign up for a Rotten Tomatoes api key. Visit http://developer.rottentomatoes.com/docs/read/Home for all the info you'll need.
Copy and paste your api key into the variable "apiKey" in rottenNetflix.js.

Open Chrome
(Windows)
Click the wrench icon and click Tools -> Extensions
Click the "Developer Mode" checkbox
Click "Load unpacked extension"
Navigate to source folder and click "OK"
Enjoy!

